					<h2 class="strap">Satanic Verses Row</h2>
		
		
			<h1 itemprop="name headline  ">War of the Word</h1>
		
					<div itemprop="description" id="stand-first" class="stand-first-alone" data-component="Article:standfirst_cta">Robin Lustig, Martin Bailey, Simon de Bruxelles and Ian Mather look at one of the most chilling episodes to engulf the world of culture in recent times<br><br><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20141008235518/http://www.observer.co.uk/race">Race in Britain - Observer special</a></div>
		
		
